{"type":"message","id":"2c2b3bee","parentId":"db8b7c2a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T20:09:37.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. Let me check what HEARTBEAT.md says I should do.\n\nLooking at HEARTBEAT.md from the context, it says:\n\n## 任务：检查并提交未保存的修改\n\n每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 目录是否有未提交的修改，如有则按功能划分 commit 并 push 到远端。\n\n### 检查步骤\n\n1. **进入工作目录**\n   ```bash\n   cd ~/.openclaw\n   ```\n\n2. **检查 git 状态**\n   ```bash\n   git status\n   ```\n\n3. **如果有未提交的修改，按以下规则分组**：\n\n   | 修改类型 | Commit 消息前缀 |\n   |----------|-----------------|\n   | 新技能/技能更新 | `skill:` |\n   | 配置文件修改 | `config:` |\n   | 工作区文件 | `workspace:` |\n   | 文档更新 | `docs:` |\n   | 其他修改 | `chore:` |\n\n4. **执行提交和推送**\n   ```bash\n   git add -A\n   git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"\n   git push\n   ```\n\n5. **记录日志**（可选）\n   - 将本次提交信息记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n### 执行频率\n- 建议：每天 1 次（如上午 9:00 或下午 15:00）\n- 手动触发也可\n\n### 注意事项\n- 如果是敏感信息（如 credentials），不要 commit\n- 优先确保重要修改已同步\n\nCurrent time is 4:09 AM - this is outside the suggested times (9:00 AM or 15:00 PM). \n\nThe hour falls outside the recommended windows, so I should skip the backup check and send HEARTBEAT_OK instead.","thinkingSignature":"e80cd684721023cd415f4239462072ac35cb8e41a3d56e0ee678114e03bff442"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":373,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":20102,"totalTokens":20511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772654969766}}
