{"type":"message","id":"58f94a1b","parentId":"763e9806","timestamp":"2026-03-05T15:47:15.510Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4mKyG2GkR3DATilMDr0F5EY5|fc_01262cad895cb7b90169a9a580ff34819e952aad73f76800a7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"===== Strategies_2020_Combined.txt =====\n   28607 /tmp/jq_strategies.1wb2f2/??????/20-strategies/Strategies_2020_Combined.txt\n=== 2020 年度策略合集 ===\r\n共包含 99 个策略文件\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n==================================================\r\nSTART OF FILE: 01 AdaptiveMA自适应均线 过滤器 期货多品种模型 收益稳定增长.txt\r\nPATH: D:\\0208\\2020年度精选策略\\01 AdaptiveMA自适应均线 过滤器 期货多品种模型 收益稳定增长.txt\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n该策略由聚宽用户分享，仅供学习交流使用。\r\n原文网址：https://www.joinquant.com/post/15565\r\n\r\n原文一般包含策略说明，如有疑问建议到原文和作者交流讨论。\r\n\r\n\r\n原文策略源码如下：\r\n\r\n# 导入函数库\r\nfrom jqdata import * \r\nimport talib \r\nfrom math import isnan\r\n\r\ndef initialize(context):\r\n    # 设置参数\r\n\n===== Strategies_2021_Combined.txt =====\n   36882 /tmp/jq_strategies.1wb2f2/??????/21-strategies/Strategies_2021_Combined.txt\n=== 2021 年度策略合集 ===\r\n共包含 99 个策略文件\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n==================================================\r\nSTART OF FILE: 0.回测提速十倍,过滤ST,退市,停牌,新股优化方法.txt\r\nPATH: D:\\0208\\2021年度精选策略\\0.回测提速十倍,过滤ST,退市,停牌,新股优化方法.txt\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n#!/usr/bin/env python\r\n# coding: utf-8\r\n\r\n# In[9]:\r\n\r\n\r\n# 过滤 ST,停牌，新股,科创板\r\ndef filter_st_paused_new(stock_list,days,context):\r\n    df = get_all_securities(types=['stock'], date=context.current_dt)\r\n    kcb=list(df[df.index.str.startswith('688')].index.unique()) # 排除科创板股票\r\n    start_date=(context.current_dt - timedelta(days=days)).date()\r\n    df_new_stock = df[df['start_date'] > start_date]\r\n    stock_list = list(set(stock_list).difference(set(df_new_stock.index)).difference(set(kcb)))\r\n    curr_data = get_current_data()\r\n    stock_list = [stock for stock in stock_list if not curr_data[stock].is_st] # 非ST 几百只\r\n\n===== Strategies_2022_Combined.txt =====\n   34819 /tmp/jq_strategies.1wb2f2/??????/22-strategies/Strategies_2022_Combined.txt\n=== 2022 年度策略合集 ===\r\n共包含 97 个策略文件\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n==================================================\r\nSTART OF FILE: 1.易方达二八轮动测试.txt\r\nPATH: D:\\0208\\2022年度精选策略\\1.易方达二八轮动测试.txt\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n# 克隆自聚宽文章：https://www.joinquant.com/post/22555\r\n# 标题：易方达二八轮动测试\r\n# 作者：子鹿\r\n\r\n# 导入函数库\r\nimport jqdata\r\nimport time\r\nimport datetime\r\n\r\n'''\r\n================================================================================\r\n总体回测前\r\n================================================================================\r\n'''\r\n#1\r\n\n===== Strategies_2023_Combined.txt =====\n   28548 /tmp/jq_strategies.1wb2f2/??????/23-strategies/Strategies_2023_Combined.txt\n=== 2023 年度策略合集 ===\r\n共包含 99 个策略文件\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n==================================================\r\nSTART OF FILE: 0.7年40倍，模拟超过两年，年化高回撤低.txt\r\nPATH: D:\\0208\\2023年度精选策略\\0.7年40倍，模拟超过两年，年化高回撤低.txt\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n# 克隆自聚宽文章：https://www.joinquant.com/post/30481\r\n# 标题：7年40倍，模拟超过两年，年化高回撤低\r\n# 作者：quakecat\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import division\r\nfrom bwlist import *\r\nimport math\r\n\r\ndef set_param():\r\n    # 交易设置\r\n    g.stocknum = 4 # 理想持股数量\r\n    g.bearpercent = 0.3 # 熊市仓位\r\n    g.bearposition = True # 熊市是否持仓\r\n    g.sellrank = 10 # 排名多少位之后(不含)卖出\r\n    g.buyrank = 9 # 排名多少位之前(含)可以买入\r\n\n===== Strategies_2024_Combined.txt =====\n   61882 /tmp/jq_strategies.1wb2f2/??????/24-strategies/Strategies_2024_Combined.txt\n=== 2024 年度策略合集 ===\r\n\r\n==================================================\r\nSTART OF FILE: 1.一颗耀眼的星—【回顾2】小市值成长股策略更新—改.txt\r\nPATH: D:\\0208\\2024年度精选策略2\\1.一颗耀眼的星—【回顾2】小市值成长股策略更新—改.txt\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n# 克隆自聚宽文章：https://www.joinquant.com/post/39325\r\n# 标题：一颗耀眼的星—【回顾2】小市值成长股策略更新—改\r\n# 作者：jqz1226\r\n\r\n# 克隆